ActEnergy Efficiency Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Energy Efficiency Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the ENERGY EFFICIENCY REGULATIONS (amendment 11) in order to contribute to the goal of clean energy and a clean environment by increasing the stringency and/or scope of existing minimum energy performance standards for seven currently regulated products and introducing minimum energy performance standards and associated reporting and compliance requirements for five new products.
